        "title": "Vision Pro and VisionOS 2 \u2014 Spatial computing roadmap",
        "body": "<p>Apple's Vision Pro and VisionOS 2 mark a milestone in spatial computing, combining immersive hardware with on-device AI and seamless software integration. The roadmap outlines upcoming developer tools, updates to spatial OS, and new experiences designed for enterprise workflows. This release continues Apple\u2019s emphasis on privacy-first processing and on-device computation, aligning with the company\u2019s long-standing design philosophy.</p><p>The Vision Pro launch, priced at $3,499, opened new avenues for enterprise collaboration and immersive product demonstrations. VisionOS 2 expands the platform with improved spatial understanding, gesture controls, and developer capabilities across Apple devices.</p><p>Read the full product and roadmap details in the official press materials and investor updates.</p>",
